{"type": "article", "id": 2379, "title": "衣架式卷筒纸架", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-16T15:14:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222239muQf7chCJgvlartY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t卷筒纸架绝对是卫生间内最容易被人忽视的装饰之一，市面上目前有的款式大多是封闭式的卫生纸架，而丹麦家居品牌 Fermliving 带来的这款新品则在物料方面尽量减少加工，利用衣架的原理设计了这款卷筒纸架，简洁的造型设计绝对会颠覆人们的传统印象，但是又不失应有的功能性。这款卷筒纸架将于 10 月 4 日上线发售，定价 30 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.fermliving.com/webshop/shop/new-collection-aw14/brass-toilet-paper-holder.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里预定</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222237Fi8ACQ6r2fkZWudE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222238Z0A927XKBIlCvsou.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}